        ECPoint multiply(ECPoint p,
                 java.math.BigInteger k)
        Multiplies the ECPoint p by k, i.e. p is added k times to itself.
        Parameters:
        p - The ECPoint to be multiplied.
        k - The factor by which p is multiplied.
        Returns:
        p multiplied by k.
